{"tid":2009622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Wechat 審核國外傳入相片   敏感相片全用戶自動屏蔽","createTime":"2020-05-10T01:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T02:26:14.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e4f728845d9cb42d9d12808795aa1e2c8e275d","tid":2009622,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:12:40.000Z","msg":"影雪<br />\n最近有研究報告指，WeChat 正在監控外國（非中國大陸）用戶的賬號，以強化其針對中國大陸用戶的檢閱系統演算法。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大多倫多大學網絡研究機構公民實驗室（Citizen Lab）在今周四（5月7日）發佈一份研究報告，指外國帳號間的通訊會被監控，並用於 WeChat 針對中國大陸賬號的審查。若其對話內容若涉政治話題，便會被添加到針對中國大陸賬號的審查列表中⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TDheTMV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTDheTMV.png&h=68061bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/05/09/wechat-censor/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F05%2F09%2Fwechat-censor%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=0a10be63\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/05/09/wechat-censor/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"976fa0d9da44bc8f75b07a1036c0f2c5d7cde2af","tid":2009622,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:14:47.000Z","msg":"審核乜鳩<br />\n根本應該全面封鎖玩單機"},{"pid":"c988a17cd6ff046b909ea24509d425f478e2f78c","tid":2009622,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:26:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">wfc<br />\n根本都唔用</span>"}]}